default2.3default              
defaultI have set a priority of putting victims at the heart of the Criminal Justice System
default.  A sustained focus on this approach has seen victim satisfaction rates increase from 86.7% to 89.2%, which also places Avon and Somerset on track to becoming a top 10 national performer by 2017.  
default&#xa0;default2.4default              defaultWe
default 
defaultstill have much work to do delivering the aspirations of the Police and Crime Plan, particularly in 
defaultincreas
